3) Create Backend S3 and create user

-> for this we need to create first s3 bucket and after that add Backend s3 terraform resource

terraform {
  backend "s3" {
    bucket = "terraform-state-sammek"
    key = "global/s3/terraform.tfstate"
    region = "us-east-1"
    encrypt = true
    profile = "terraform"
  }
}

